quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  11,50,WE ‘ILA ‘ADIN ‘EHAHUM HUDÆN KALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU ‘IN ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA MUFTERUNE
  11,51,JA KAWMI LA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI ‘EXHRÆN ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALEL-LEDHI FETERENI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  11,52,WE JA KAWMI ESTEGFIRU REBBEKUM THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI JURSILI ES-SEMA’E ‘ALEJKUM MIDRARÆN WE JEZIDKUM KUWETEN ‘ILA KUWETIKUM WE LA TETEWELLEW MUXHRIMINE
  11,53,KALU JA HUDU MA XHI’TENA BIBEJJINETIN WE MA NEHNU BITARIKI ‘ALIHETINA ‘AN KAWLIKE WE MA NEHNU LEKE BIMU’UMININE
  11,54,‘IN NEKULU ‘ILLA A’TERAKE BA’DU ‘ALIHETINA BISU’IN KALE ‘INNI ‘USH/HIDU ELLAHE WE ESH/HEDU ‘ENNI BERI’UN MIMMA TUSHRIKUNE
  11,55,MIN DUNIHI FEKIDUNI XHEMI’ÆN THUMME LA TUNDHIRUNI
  11,56,‘INNI TEWEKKELTU ‘ALA ELLAHI RABBI WE RABBIKUM MA MIN DABBETIN ‘ILLA HUWE ‘AHIDHUN BINASIJETIHA ‘INNE RABBI ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  11,57,FE’IN TEWELLEW FEKAD ‘EBLEGTUKUM MA ‘URSILTU BIHI ‘ILEJKUM WE JESTEHLIFU RABBI KAWMÆN GAJREKUM WE LA TEDURRUNEHU SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNE RABBI ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN HEFIDHUN
  11,58,WE LEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA NEXHXHEJNA HUDÆN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU BIREHMETIN MINNA WE NEXHXHEJNAHUM MIN ‘ADHABIN GALIDHIN
  11,59,WE TILKE ‘ADUN XHEHEDU BI’AJATI RABBIHIM WE ‘ASEW RUSULEHU WE ETTEBA’U ‘EMRE KULLI XHEBBARIN ‘ANIDIN
  11,60,WE ‘UTBI’U FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA LA’NETEN WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘ELA ‘INNE ‘ADÆN KEFERU REBBEHUM ‘ELA BU’DÆN LI’ADIN KAWMI HUDIN